# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:34
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_8b40ce2d:

    # "She gets in the car wearing a pretty dress and a wig."
    "她身着漂亮连衣裙，戴着假发上了车。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:37
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_c178e9aa:

    # bn "Oh, thank you."
    bn "哦，谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:38
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_c91b3eb2:

    # bn "I sometimes like to wear it when I'm going out on a nice date."
    bn "有时去约会时，我喜欢戴上它。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:39
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_c295710b:

    # bn "Not that I've had many dates."
    bn "虽然我约会次数不多。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:40
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_a71bf22a:

    # pc "Well it's very pretty."
    pc "嗯，这假发真的很漂亮。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:41
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_3dc0e34e:

    # "She turns away and blushes a little."
    "她转过头去，脸颊微微泛红。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:43
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_313b6a1f:

    # bn "Oh, um. I don't know."
    bn "哦，呃……我也不知道。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:44
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_2f29693a:

    # bn "I like to wear them when I go out somewhere nice."
    bn "我去漂亮的地方时喜欢戴它。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:47
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_1431cc27:

    # bn "Thank you."
    bn "谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:48
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_3dc0e34e_1:

    # "She turns away and blushes a little."
    "她转过头去，脸颊微微泛红。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:50
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_563fa2c8:

    # bn "Okay. Well I prefer the wig when I go somewhere nice."
    bn "好吧。其实我去漂亮的地方时更喜欢戴假发。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:51
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_e256026f:

    # "I'm not really sure how to respond, so we end up driving the rest of the way to the restaurant in an awkward silence."
    "我实在不知道该怎么回应，于是剩下的路程里，我们便在尴尬的沉默中开车前往餐厅。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:54
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_62345451:

    # "When we get to Luigi's, we sit and order our meals."
    "到了路易吉餐厅，我们坐下并点了餐。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:55
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_c57a5228:

    # "Then we chat for a while."
    "然后我们聊了一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:58
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_0875967f:

    # "The server brings our food out, and we continue talking while we eat."
    "服务员把菜端上来，我们边吃边继续聊。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:60
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_dbe7b11f:

    # "When we're done eating, we just hang around and talk for a little more."
    "吃完后，我们又闲坐着聊了一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Juliana/JulianaDates/julianaluigisdate.rpy:63
translate chinese julianaluigisstartdate_018a4945:

    # "After our conversation, I pay for the food and we leave the restaurant and drive back to Juliana's house."
    "聊完后，我结了账，我们离开餐厅，开车回朱莉安娜家。"

